To run HOL-light, type `holrun'. Then, in CAML, type:

include "hol.ml";;

This will load all the system from scratch (it takes several minutes).
If you don't need the whole system, you can edit out parts of
${PREFIX}/lib/caml-light/hol.ml
which indicates the build sequence.

===========================================================================
